  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Alice发起交易邀请的时序图。Alice作为外部参与者，先调用offer-up.contract的makeTradeInvitation方法，然后合约再通知Zoe。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "Zoe",
        "makeTradeInvitation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Alice和Zoe需要放在不同颜色的box里区分吗？还有合约本身要不要单独用一个box？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "Zoe",
        "offer-up.contract"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Alice用aqua色，Zoe用darksalmon，合约用skyblue单独一个Contract盒子。这样角色边界清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "Zoe",
        "offer-up.contract"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，三个box已经画好了。那第一条消息是Alice异步调用合约的makeTradeInvitation对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "makeTradeInvitation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，然后合约要激活，再异步发消息给Zoe的makeInvitation，传入tradeHandler参数。Zoe收到后要返回一个invitation给合约。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "offer-up.contract",
        "Zoe",
        "makeInvitation",
        "tradeHandler",
        "invitation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Zoe返回invitation之后，合约再把这个Invitation toJoin发给Alice。然后Alice向Zoe发起offer，带上toJoin、proposal和Price参数？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "Alice",
        "Invitation toJoin",
        "offer",
        "toJoin",
        "proposal",
        "Price"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，而且Zoe收到offer后要做一个内部处理——escrow Price pmt，就是托管价格支付。最后Zoe调用合约的tradeHandler，传入buyerSeat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe",
        "escrow Price pmt",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "tradeHandler",
        "buyerSeat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我检查了一下，Zoe的escrow是内部自循环消息，tradeHandler是返回给合约的最后一步，所有激活和销毁的生命周期也都对齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
